cs5031.catalogplayer.catalog
Interface Album

All Superinterfaces:
Resource
All Known Implementing Classes:
MyAlbum
public interface Album
extends Resource

Describes an album in a Catalog. An album has a title and artist entries to describe the album as a whole. A set of URLs are associated with it such as the resource URL that points to further information about the album (defined in Resource), a base URL that provides the basis for finding the artefacts that make up the album, a URL for an image representing the album and a URL for the licence under which the music has been published. An album can be 'tagged' and, finally, has a list of tracks that it consists of.

Author:
avoss
